desc-string: Nestled within the lush foliage of the jungle, it's like a miracle on the earth. Its rocky peaks resemble a row of sharp sword blades, yet they also resemble petals.
punishDesc-string: When you die, there's a chance to drop the items in your backpack.

desc-string:
In that shattered domain, a dark fortress stands proudly, its edges suspended amidst the void, devoid of any physical support. It is filled with a large number of dangerous monsters, growing many rare collectibles that have never been seen before.
Recommended team: 3 warriors, 1 collector
punishDesc-string: When you die, there's a chance to drop the items in your backpack.

desc-string: Battle against fiery creatures; fight in the dark and eerie environment, guarding against attacks from void beings; delve into ancient ruins to unearth secrets and treasures hidden deep within. Brave adventurers, are you ready to face this challenge?
punishDesc-string: When you die, there's a chance to drop the items in your backpack.

desc-string:
Rewards
- Defeating Monsters or Gathering: Players will receive LUAUSD rewards invested by totems.
- Eliminating Other Players: Players can claim the unsettled LUASUD rewards of their defeated opponents.
- Defeating Bosses: Players may obtain mysterious special materials essential for game progression.
Rules Overview
- Level Structure: The dungeon consists of 3 chaotic levels, each presenting its own set of challenges.
- Safe Zones: There are safe zones within the levels, which will shrink over time, forcing players into confrontation.
- Three Types of Gates:
 - Challenge Gate: For the brave, this gate leads to the next level of adventure.
 - Escape Gate: Exit the dungeon and forfeit any unsettled LUAUSD rewards.
 - Settlement Gate: Settle and collect LUAUSD rewards at a certain ratio.
punishDesc-string: When you die, there's a chance to drop the items in your backpack.

desc-string: Daily Challenge - The Daily challenge copy is divided into nine layers, each layer corresponds to each level of monsters, after completing the challenge will get the level reward, death will not have any drop, copy tickets from the daily quest
PVEP Training Ground - Support 12-24 player battles, death will not have any drops, tickets from daily missions

desc-string:
The challengers who complete the challenge will have the opportunity to receive a medal reward.
In the Gathering Challenge, the defense of the Resource will be increased. Correspondingly, players will receive a buff that converts gathering proficiency into gathering attack.
